    "markdown": {
      "text": "## Contents\n\n1. Computer - My Friend 1-6\n\n2. My Friend-ASmart Machine 7-14\n\n3. Computer-A Handy Machine ___ 15-22\n\n4. Know My Friend 23-36\n\n5. Connect with Computer-1 37-50\n\n6. Do's and Don'ts of a Computer\n\n### In this book Look out for these...\n\n\n\n<table border=1 style='margin: auto; word-wrap: break-word;'><tr><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Big Question <img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_100_859_175_929.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"\" /></td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Question to generate curiosity and learn more about a concept</td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Fun with Friends <img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_617_849_744_912.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"\" /></td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Group activities for students to do in the class connecting with Art</td></tr><tr><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Learning Steps <img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_99_1000_178_1068.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"\" /></td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Objectives of the chapter</td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Word Master <img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_620_1004_721_1078.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"\" /></td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Contains new/ difficult words with their meanings for building vocabulary</td></tr><tr><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Let&#x27;s have Fun <img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_98_1158_178_1229.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"\" /></td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Recap questions for students to attempt</td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_618_1108_710_1140.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"\" /> <img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_621_1151_713_1231.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"\" /></td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Knowledge and comprehension based questions</td></tr><tr><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_84_1258_223_1290.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"\" /> <img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_110_1298_186_1386.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"\" /></td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Facts and important information</td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_619_1257_744_1290.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"\" /> <img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_624_1291_717_1377.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"\" /></td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Application based questions</td></tr><tr><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Twister TWISTER</td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Fun activities/questions like riddles and puzzles</td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_622_1407_756_1439.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"\" /> <img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_624_1445_719_1531.jpg\" alt=\"Image\"\" /></td><td style='text-align: center; word-wrap: break-word;'>Analytical questions</td></tr></table>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_1133_346_1169_390.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"3%\" /></div>\n\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_97_1453_216_1542.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"10%\" /></div>\n",
